## See Scintilla.iface for documentation
## This file can be used to define additional features for the editor interface
## The "use" keyword overrides subsequent definitions

cat Overrides

# CallTipPosStart was changed from fun to get in Scintilla 5.5.7, which broke the naming convention
use get position CallTipPosStart=2203(,) -> fun position CallTipPosStart=2203(,)
